![Modrinth](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ed649d88bc4a563f15205f231c830006904f3576.png)

**Some of the mods, based on the Modpack officially released on CurseForge, due to rights and copyright issues, are not included in this Modpack on Modrinth, so some of the experiences or future versions of this Modpack will not have them or I will probably remove them from the ModPack! Sorry about that, but it's beyond my control!**

![Attention](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/94b938f603a87283650f7b0c70f01eeb8fa2bd16.png)

**All these mods are not my work, and I have no rights over them! So, I took all these mods from CurseForge and Modrinth to create a Modpack and make it easy and optimized for everyone who wants to play it! Hope you understand it !**

