# Attention !
This ModPack is included with **Better Combat** and **First Person**. When First person mod is _activated_, if you press _'R'_ on your keyboard, the **Better Combat** _broke_, because the button _'R'_ change your perspective on **Better combat** to _improve your abilities_. So, how can i solve it? Removing the mod can be a great solution but a little hard, so you can press _'F6'_ to **desactive** the **first person perspective** to use the **Better combat** issues. If you want to activate the **First Person** again, **just press** _'F6'_.

