**Let's see the performance recomendations !**

![Performance](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/60ea49f2104498191dc3c443e63d00d6c030be21.png)

# RX 580

Render distance 8 or low.
Complementary - Low - You can try medium, but not recommended.
BSL - Medium or low.
Fresh Animations able !
If you want more performance, desactive!

# RX 5500 XT

Render distance 12 - 15.
Complementary - Medium.
BSL - High.
Fresh Animations and all other resources able !
If you Want more performance, just able Fresh Animations
and Recolorful Containers GUI, for better experience!

These are my recommendations, but it really depends on your computer (processor, brand of parts...).
Good Luck! :)

**I hope you like it!**

